@startuml component_diagram
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Lab Booking System - Component Diagram (D2)

actor "Student/Faculty/Researcher/Guest" as EndUser
actor "Lab Manager" as Manager
actor "Head Lab Coordinator" as Coordinator

component "GUI Layer\n(lab.gui)" as GUI
component "Application Services\n(lab.service)" as Service
component "Domain Model\n(lab.model)" as Model
component "Pattern Modules\n(lab.pattern.*)" as Patterns
component "Data Access Layer\n(lab.data repositories)" as Data
component "CSV Storage\n(runtime-data/*.csv)" as CSV
component "External Payment Systems\n(simulated adapters)" as PaymentExt
component "Sensor Source\n(manager sensor update workflow)" as SensorExt

EndUser --> GUI : register/login/book/modify/cancel/extend/check-in
Manager --> GUI : manage equipment/sensor logs
Coordinator --> GUI : approve users/create managers

GUI --> Service : booking operations
GUI --> Patterns : factory/singleton/proxy usage
Service --> Patterns : adapter/decorator usage
Service --> Data : read/write domain state
Patterns --> Data : proxy real access, singleton user creation path
Data --> CSV : persist entities
Patterns --> PaymentExt : adapter dispatch
SensorExt --> Data : sensor log entries

note right of GUI
Responsibilities:
- screen flow
- role-specific dashboard routing
- user interactions
end note

note right of Service
Responsibilities:
- booking rules
- overlap checks
- deposit and extension billing
- check-in timing logic
end note

note right of Data
Responsibilities:
- repository operations
- CSV serialization
- loading seed/runtime data
end note

@enduml
